=== 美國 ===
恩潘納達，在[[紐約市|紐約市]]和整個[[新澤西州|新澤西州]]的食物推車，速食卡車和餐館中廣泛提供販賣。<ref>[http://gothamist.com/2014/10/13/nyc_empanada_guide.php "10 Spots To Score Excellent Empanadas In NYC"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708091422/http://gothamist.com/2014/10/13/nyc_empanada_guide.php |date=2016-07-08 }} by Angely Mercado, ''[[Gothamist|Gothamist]]'', 13 October 2014;<br />[http://newyork.cbslocal.com/2015/10/09/nyc-food-truck-lunch-empanadas-from-la-sonrisa-empanadas/ "NYC Food Truck Lunch: Empanadas From La Sonrisa Empanadas"] {{Wayback|url=http://newyork.cbslocal.com/2015/10/09/nyc-food-truck-lunch-empanadas-from-la-sonrisa-empanadas/ |date=20210224031735 }} by Perry R., [[CBS_New_York|CBS New York]], 9 October 2015</ref>恩潘納達通常販賣在擁有大量西班牙裔人口的美國地區，如[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]，[[聖安東尼奧_(德克薩斯州)|聖安東尼奧]]，<ref>{{cite web|title=The 15 Best Places for Empanadas in San Antonio|url=https://foursquare.com/top-places/san-antonio/best-places-empanadas|website=FourSquare|accessdate=January 4, 2017|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308171448/https://foursquare.com/top-places/san-antonio/best-places-empanadas|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Rice|first1=Janae|title=Finding Empanadas in SA|url=http://www.sacurrent.com/Flavor/archives/2014/04/08/finding-empanadas-in-sa|work=[[San_Antonio_Current|San Antonio Current]]|accessdate=January 4, 2017|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225084414/https://www.sacurrent.com/Flavor/archives/2014/04/08/finding-empanadas-in-sa|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Chabala|first1=Tracy|title=5 Great Baked Empanadas in Los Angeles|url=http://www.laweekly.com/restaurants/5-great-baked-empanadas-in-los-angeles-2895481|work=[[LA_Weekly|LA Weekly]]|accessdate=January 4, 2017|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330111825/https://www.laweekly.com/restaurants/5-great-baked-empanadas-in-los-angeles-2895481|dead-url=no}}</ref>

